That's true.

7
00:00:21,273 --> 00:00:24,512
It's better to be more cautious regarding such matters.<br>GIve it to me.

8
00:00:31,477 --> 00:00:32,468
Niang Niang.

9
00:00:33,797 --> 00:00:35,334
You haven't drunk your pregnancy medication.

10
00:00:36,804 --> 00:00:40,048
When I sent it to you just now, you said it was too hot.<br>Now it's just warm.

11
00:00:40,176 --> 00:00:41,636
If we leave it any longer, it'll turn cold.

12
00:01:17,654 --> 00:01:18,587
Your Majesty.

13
