Logically, it's right, but emotionally speaking,

22
00:02:06,500 --> 00:02:09,100
Empress must really hate me.

23
00:02:13,600 --> 00:02:15,100
I gifted you the Childbirth Guanyin

24
00:02:15,700 --> 00:02:18,100
in the hope that you would be at peace

25
00:02:18,312 --> 00:02:21,312
and not become distracted. The most important thing right now

26
00:02:21,423 --> 00:02:23,716
is to bear a child for the Emperor.

27
00:02:25,877 --> 00:02:29,797
Whether or not I'll be able to give birth,<br>is all in the hands of the Empress,

28
00:02:29,910 --> 00:02:31,402
not me.

29
00:02:32,729 --> 00:02:34,248
What do you mean?

30
00:02:34,391 --> 00:02:36,133
Isn't that the case?

31
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:41,700
According to Niang Niang's wishes, the child lives. Against Niang Niang's wishes, both the mother and the child are ruined.

32
00:02:42,164 --> 00:02:43,784
For so many years,

33
